ия вклада в течение нового срока действуют ставки для дополнительных взносов на дату продления. </li><li>Количество продлений не ограничено. </li></ul></div></div></div><div style="margin-top: 24px;"><div class="depprol depprol_top_extra depprol_bottom_extra"><div class="kitt-grid kitt-grid_fixed"><div class="kitt-row"><div class="kitt-col kitt-col_xs_12"><h1 class="dk-sbol-heading dk-sbol-heading_size_sm dk-sbol-heading_grey">Условия продления СберВклада и СберВклада Прайм </h1></div></div></div><div class="kitt-grid kitt-grid_fixed depprol__wrap"><div class="kitt-row"><div class="kitt-col kitt-col_xs_12"><div class="depprol-menu"><div class="depprol-menu__inputs"><div class="dk-sbol-field depprol-menu__input"><div class="dk-sbol-field__row"><label id="tMG1-kFIR2Ie7Ud1JHCey-label" for="tMG1-kFIR2Ie7Ud1JHCey" class="dk-sbol-label dk-sbol-label_size_md dk-sbol-field__label dk-sbol-field__label_size_md"><span class="depprol-menu__hint">Дата открытия </span></label></div></div><div class="dk-sbol-field depprol-menu__input"><div class="dk-sbol-field__row"><label id="lDbHjYHUjxFQvYzy9RPzA-label" for="lDbHjYHUjxFQvYzy9RPzA" class="dk-sbol-label dk-sbol-label_size_md dk-sbol-field__label dk-sbol-field__label_size_md"><span class="depprol-menu__hint">Дата продления </span></label></div></div><button data-test-id="Button-primary-md" class="dk-sbol-button dk-sbol-button_type_primary dk-sbol-button_size_md depprol-menu__button depprol-menu__button_desktop" tabindex="0"><span class="dk-sbol-button__content"><span class="dk-sbol-button__text dk-sbol-button__text_size_md">Показать ставки </span></span></button></div><div class="depprol-menu__checkboxes"><div class="dk-sbol-field depprol-menu__checkbox"><div class="dk-sbol-field__row dk-sbol-field__row_inline"><label id="pYh6QSEhx1VivGhCXk-Bk-label" for="pYh6QSEhx1VivGhCXk-Bk" class="dk-sbol-label dk-sbol-label_size_md dk-sbol-field__label dk-sbol-field__label_inline_last dk-sbol-field__label_size_md">У меня был СберВклад Прайм </ ия вклада в течение нового срока действуют ставки для дополнительных взносов на дату продления. </li><li>Количество продлений не ограничено. </li></ul></div></div></div><div style="margin-top: 24px;"><div class="depprol depprol_top_extra depprol_bottom_extra"><div class="kitt-grid kitt-grid_fixed"><div class="kitt-row"><div class="kitt-col kitt-col_xs_12"><h1 class="dk-sbol-heading dk-sbol-heading_size_sm dk-sbol-heading_grey">Условия продления СберВклада и СберВклада Прайм </h1></div></div></div><div class="kitt-grid kitt-grid_fixed depprol__wrap"><div class="kitt-row"><div class="kitt-col kitt-col_xs_12"><div class="depprol-menu"><div class="depprol-menu__inputs"><div class="dk-sbol-field depprol-menu__input"><div class="dk-sbol-field__row"><label id="rU6lx7ueqRwAXwlivZlca-label" for="rU6lx7ueqRwAXwlivZlca" class="dk-sbol-label dk-sbol-label_size_md dk-sbol-field__label dk-sbol-field__label_size_md"><span class="depprol-menu__hint">Дата открытия </span></label></div></div><div class="dk-sbol-field depprol-menu__input"><div class="dk-sbol-field__row"><label id="X-G7DEi2K4gKnwwV7tazm-label" for="X-G7DEi2K4gKnwwV7tazm" class="dk-sbol-label dk-sbol-label_size_md dk-sbol-field__label dk-sbol-field__label_size_md"><span class="depprol-menu__hint">Дата продления </span></label></div></div><button data-test-id="Button-primary-md" class="dk-sbol-button dk-sbol-button_type_primary dk-sbol-button_size_md depprol-menu__button depprol-menu__button_desktop" tabindex="0"><span class="dk-sbol-button__content"><span class="dk-sbol-button__text dk-sbol-button__text_size_md">Показать ставки </span></span></button></div><div class="depprol-menu__checkboxes"><div class="dk-sbol-field depprol-menu__checkbox"><div class="dk-sbol-field__row dk-sbol-field__row_inline"><label id="p9uRXLYPfD4hP3hxXSvFU-label" for="p9uRXLYPfD4hP3hxXSvFU" class="dk-sbol-label dk-sbol-label_size_md dk-sbol-field__label dk-sbol-field__label_inline_last dk-sbol-field__label_size_md">У меня был СберВклад Прайм </
